1.30	Lando_Calrissian_and_the_Mindharp_of_Sharu	Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu	Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu is a science fiction novel set in the Star Wars Expanded Universe. It was written by L. Neil Smith and originally published in 1983 by Del Rey, a division of Ballantine Books. It is the first of three books in The Adventures of Lando Calrissian trilogy (the other two books in the series are Lando Calrissian and the Flamewind of Oseon and Lando Calrissian and the Starcave of ThonBoka), and one of the oldest Expanded Universe works. It is set prior to the events of A New Hope.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c6/Lando_mindharpofsharu.jpg/200px-Lando_mindharpofsharu.jpg
